{"tid":2007872,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(集思廣益)一人一樣泛民議員必食嘅食物","createTime":"2020-05-08T15:05:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T15:27:48.000Z","uid":103514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fa5aaea4d1c8c731db8148b00bb27ea9842a13eb","tid":2007872,"uid":103514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T15:05:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bHATdsB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbHATdsB.jpg&h=c6b87629&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家知道開會好攰架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一定要食啲野補充體力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過每個人對唔同食物都有唔同口味(好似榴槤咁)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能有啲人會覺得好香呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以既然咁憎(aka.唔擅長)暴力場面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如選擇be water喇，我指食飯方面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/A_4r0RQv76s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FA_4r0RQv76s&d=ZKl1Acg0IOD8KmAOqHMUQGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=3c878c62\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/A_4r0RQv76s</a><br />\n<br />\n順便幫arm channel share下啲片"},{"pid":"abde4cd633ca17d83e60dcaf6fd61a8f0ef3228c","tid":2007872,"uid":49183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T15:07:02.000Z","msg":"家庭裝汽水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"191cdb3f12103a274a5620031747e8b0cd73d111","tid":2007872,"uid":292674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T15:27:48.000Z","msg":"呀嫲既奶水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}